<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTETanner198791-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTETanner198791_6-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFTanner1987">Tanner 1987</a>, p.&#160;91.</span>
