<li id="cite_note-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-39">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFPalmer2014" class="citation journal cs1">Palmer, Grant H. (2014). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20160716234415/http://www.jwha.website/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Journal_14-1.pdf">"Joseph Smith, Captain Kidd, Cumorah, and Moroni"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i>John Whitmer Historical Association Journal</i>. <b>34</b> (1): 50–57. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.jwha.website/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Journal_14-1.pdf">the original</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span> on 16 July 2016<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">24 May</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=John+Whitmer+Historical+Association+Journal&amp;rft.atitle=Joseph+Smith%2C+Captain+Kidd%2C+Cumorah%2C+and+Moroni&amp;rft.volume=34&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=50-57&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft.aulast=Palmer&amp;rft.aufirst=Grant+H.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jwha.website%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2FJournal_14-1.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACriticism+of+the+Book+of+Mormon" class="Z3988"></span></span>
