<li id="cite_note-Cowan-46"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Cowan_46-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFCowan1997" class="citation cs2">Cowan, Marvin (1997), <i>Mormon Claims Answered</i> (2nd&#160;ed.), M.W. Cowan, <a href="/wiki/ASIN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ASIN (identifier)">ASIN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0006E7Z2G">B0006E7Z2G</a></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Mormon+Claims+Answered&amp;rft.edition=2nd&amp;rft.pub=M.W.+Cowan&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0006E7Z2G%23id-name%3DASIN&amp;rft.aulast=Cowan&amp;rft.aufirst=Marvin&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACriticism+of+the+Book+of+Mormon" class="Z3988"></span></span>
